This is a game designed and implemented by myself using Unity3D engine. Although it is made for mobile platform, Unity also support web and pc builds.

To Play:

Click on 1 of the 4 shapes to select a power
Click again to place selected shape on map
When cat enter the shape, it will be able to do different movement such as adjusting direction, bouncing back, teleporting and attacking enemies.

Enemies also move and attack in different patterns